l.org/2014/03/week-compatible-reveal-aria-reatro-colangine/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:78:"http://wpml.org/2014/03/week-compatible-reveal-aria-reatro-colangine/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Fri, 14 Mar 2014 15:55:19 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:22:"Compatibility Bulletin";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"http://wpml.org/?p=359271";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:332:"Today we are happy to announce that we have another 3 themes to add to our compatibility list. The themes are Reveal, Aria, Colangine If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here: Multilingual Ready Themes Multilingual Ready Plugins Also, if you&#8217;re a [&#8230;]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:10:"Amit Kvint";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4118:"<p>Today we are happy to announce that we have another 3 themes to add to our compatibility list. The themes are <a title="Reveal theme" href="http://themetrust.com/themes/reveal" target="_blank">Reveal</a>, <a title="Aria theme &amp; WPML" href="http://themeforest.net/item/aria-pure-business-theme/5124079" target="_blank">Aria</a>, <a title="colangine theme &amp; WPML" href="http://themeforest.net/item/colangine-creative-flat-wordpress-theme/6022530" target="_blank">Colangine</a></p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a title="Multilingual Ready Themes " href="http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a title="Multilingual Ready Plugins " href="http://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you&#8217;re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href="http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a title="Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins" href="http://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin <strong>Multilingual Ready</strong>.</p>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Reveal theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themetrust.com/themes/reveal"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493" alt="ekho" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Screen-Shot-2014-03-14-at-16.07.05-e1394807523847.png" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Reveal is a responsive portfolio theme that’s designed to look great no matter the device or screen size on which it’s viewed. Its minimal and clean styling paired with Ajax powered project viewing make this theme perfect for showing off your best work.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themetrust.com/themes/reveal">Purchase Reveal</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Aria theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/aria-pure-business-theme/5124079/"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493" alt="ekho" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Screen-Shot-2014-03-14-at-16.10.50.png" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Take control of WordPress and explore tons of options that will certainly furfill your needs. Supporting unlimited colors, blogs, portfolios, sliders, team members and sidebars the theme will fit any content. Featuring also premium plugins: Revolution Slider and Visual Composer to ease the custom page creation process.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/aria-pure-business-theme/5124079/" target="_blank">Purchase Aria</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Colangine theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/colangine-creative-flat-wordpress-theme/6022530"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-340493" alt="ekho" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Screen-Shot-2014-03-14-at-16.12.24.png" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Colangine is a Creative Flat design WordPress theme, It’s Fully Responsive, Clean and Corporate Friendly with Powerful theme options, RTL Language Support and WPML multi-lingual plugin support.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/colangine-creative-flat-wordpress-theme/6022530" target="_blank">Purchase Colangina</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature"></div>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commen